data.description: Enjoy this beautiful villa located in The Villages of Longwood. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and garage. Tile and laminate throughout with open and functional layout. Kitchen appliances are stainless steel. New fridge. The owner's suite is spacious and has a large walk-in closet and dual sinks in the ensuite bath. Large screened patio that is fenced for privacy and comes with a Sunsetter awning. Accordion shutters for hurricane protection. A/C= 2019 and water heater= 2022. Garage door opener was just replaced with a Smart system and has a 10 year warranty. Keyless entry. The community amenities include two pools, a clubhouse, sidewalks and street lights. Centrally located less than 5 miles to I95 and 2 miles to downtown. HOA fee includes building insurance.
